    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a concourse-grade FD3S RX-7, featuring the legendary 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine. This example maintains its factory-spec 50/50 weight distribution and sophisticated aluminum double-wishbone suspension geometry. The drivetrain is impeccable, with a crisp 5-speed manual transmission feeding power through a Torsen LSD. Mechanical integrity is paramount; the complex vacuum system has been meticulously serviced to ensure seamless boost transition between the primary and secondary Hitachi HT12 turbos. The chassis remains rigid and free of oxidation, while the interior retains its factory-fresh tactile feel with zero bolster wear. A true turn-key masterpiece for the discerning collector.",
