      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true time-capsule 2012 Porsche 911 Carrera in showroom condition. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen rain or snow. The exterior finish is flawless, featuring its original paint with a deep, glass-like luster protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are absolutely no stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in 'as-new' condition, with the premium leather upholstery showing zero bolster wear and retaining its original factory scent. Every switch, dial, and electronic component functions perfectly. Mechanically, this 911 is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive service portfolio from authorized dealers. It recently underwent a major four-year service interval including spark plugs, drive belts, and all fluid flushes. The undercarriage is as clean as the body, with no leaks or corrosion. Included in the sale are all original keys, the complete owner\u2019s manual set, a custom indoor car cover, and a folder containing every service receipt since new. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector to acquire a late-model classic that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor.",
